title: [Whistler's Pass, Creek Bank]
description: Set just off the trail through the tall grass is a gently flowing creek.  Crystal clear water, sparkling with reflected starlight, flows barely ankle-deep in the creek bed.  The trail heads to the northeast, descending into the creek by way of a small path.
